    <briefdescription>
<para>DC motor controller for H-bridge drivers. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Controls direction + speed via two GPIO pins (or one PWM + one dir pin). Supports soft start/stop ramps to limit inrush current and mechanical stress. Provides a <ref refid="structSYN__MotorOutput" kindref="compound">SYN_MotorOutput</ref> interface for use with syn_motor_ctrl.</para>
